name: Portrait of Bobi the Cat #01
description:
Hajimemashite!

Bobi is a fat, cute, 5.5 kg, 6 years old-ish male, short-haired tabby cat, with medium length tail.

He's a stray and adopt later by me and my wife since the first time we're lived together. 

This token is a series of portrait that taken during the second year he lived with us. Basking in the golden hour sun from our little studio apartment in the southern Jakarta capital, Indonesia.
